Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come watch, it's time for the appearance{\i0}\N{\i1}of the three leaves! (yay){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:18.85,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Three Leaves, Three Colors"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning! I'll have three bowls{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Did you eat, eat, eat, eat up your{\i0}\N{\i1}feminine charm along with your food?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, wait, wait a minute! I'm bad at P.E....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(I heard something good--{\i0}\N{\i1}I've found her weakness... Sorry){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I really want is to have fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my f-r-i-e-n-d-s!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Try talking about silly things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:47.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like our love lives and other stuff like that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have any friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"My, you are direct!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're arrogant{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And high-handed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...etc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"You have no reservations, do you?!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:01:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are the three leaves running wild?!{\i0}\N{\i1}No one can stop them!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it was called "Miso"\Nor "Malt" or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:12.32,Main,,0,0,0,,To keep the nasty pests from staring,\Nwe'll be quick and stealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Ready, set!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, I, my, ambiguous me! (Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind's asleep... (zzz...){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel refreshed! Oh, really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the three of us (fever!){\i0}\N{\i1}we have transcendent wisdom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:26.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when we're actually together, it's just noisy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(One more time!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look! Going my way forcefully forward! (Go! Go!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forward! Yeah, going my way up! (Jump! Jump!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Full speed ahead!{\i0}\N{\i1}Thanks for your hard work{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the story of my (wow!){\i0}\N{\i1}kind of strange and unusual{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Best and strongest life in history{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave her alone or Satan will burst out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure this is a high school girl's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}School life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:11.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.05,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:17.59,Main,,0,0,0,,The beach is a must during summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:19.68,Main,,0,0,0,,It was worth waking up early for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Viewing the ocean from a train\Nlike this is a first for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, because you're a rich girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.60,Main,,0,0,0,,She {\i1}was {\i0}one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,At the beach, we've got to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Relax on the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Make sandcastles?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:36.36,Main,,0,0,0,,And split a watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.09,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:50.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,We came here to work, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,"Veggies, Meat, Meat, Meat, Meat, Meat, Meat, and Fish"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:05.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer. Summer means the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,The ocean means a beach hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:13.23,Main,,0,0,0,,This August, I present Himitsu\Nno Hanazono, beach hut version!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It's tough working there as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,And now she has a beach hut version.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:23.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Mitsugu found\Nthis suitable place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Always there to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, the shop is temporarily closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not what we were worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, I've been wondering since earlier,\Nbut what's "Himitsu no Hanazono"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,--It's the name of my shop.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:48.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Secret Garden... is English for\N"Himitsu no Hanazono!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you know, Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,She would know the name of where she works.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:04:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Er... well, I thought it was called "Miso"\Nor "Malt" or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:04.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Those are totally wrong.\NIt's a western cake shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if it were based on Miss Sonobe,\Nit should be called "Den of Thieves"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,...or "Shop of Chaos."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,As I said, it's "Himitsu no Hanazono!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Same difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,It's completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,It's perfect for someone who reeks of the 80's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yamaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.14,Main,,0,0,0,,So you knew, Yamaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:29.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Every time I get a receipt,\NI cringe with embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, from today we'll be\NHimitsu no Hanazono, beach hut version!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:37.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,What is a beach hut?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:50.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right. Of course\NMiss Yoko wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a rich girl who knows\Nnothing of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:57.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I have at least {\i1}heard {\i0}of it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:00.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I just do not know what it is exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe! Explain to me what\Na beach hut is in plain terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,With interpretive dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:17.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I do not understand. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I do not think I can work then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Sand! I am sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it a ritual or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:47.89,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, we've come all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,And she said she would pay us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose there is no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, let us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:05.12,Main,,0,0,0,,--Truthfully, I didn't approve of this beach hut thing.\N--I'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.87,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing good about getting\Nsunburned and heat stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,To keep the nasty pests from staring,\Nwe'll be quick and stealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.75,Main,,0,0,0,,"Shaved Ice"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,And I was playing--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:25.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yum! What is this? It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:27.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll have the melon and orange one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I want to try all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that? It sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to try it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious she's a fake customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:46.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, as usual, I'm forced to help out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Please work hard so nasty pests\Ndon't notice Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:06.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it? You seem dissatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:09.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you look different\Nfrom what I had imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:13.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I had imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer! Under the bright sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.69,Main,,0,0,0,,A summer time for girls bursting with youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:27.61,Main,,0,0,0,,The sweet lure of a flushed body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,A sweets paradise by the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:39.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Himitsu no Hanazono. Open this\Nsummer at the beach hut. Mwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Old-fashioned, as usual. And you could\Nget sued for that disguise at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.76,Main,,0,0,0,,If you could at least wear\Nsomething like Hayama or Futaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I do not wish to get an unsightly tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:58.81,Main,,0,0,0,,How about working in a bikini to avoid that?\NI'll make your uniform a bikini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Sonobe, {\i1}you {\i0}can wear a bikini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,This place is more like a\Nfancy café than a beach hut, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That's true. We'll have a summer menu\Nwith gelato, frappés, and gelatin desserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.78,Main,,0,0,0,,What about ramen?! Curry?! Fried noodles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.79,Main,,0,0,0,,We're a dessert shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't fried noodles a dessert?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.46,Main,,0,0,0,,What? It's not a side dish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:23.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Himitsu no Hanazono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,"Beach Hut"\NHimitsu no Hanazono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:29.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Open today. Himitsu no Hanazono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:32.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Beach hut, Himitsu no Hanazono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:36.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, the shop's name is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Should we move somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:46.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sister! Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:50.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:05.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard that you were working at a\Nbeach hut. I'll help with the sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll just have some of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:11.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? But the whole menu is ice cream and drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:17.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Need some help there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm cold after eating so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You do not have to push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--But, you made this. I'll finish it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:34.99,Main,,0,0,0,,--But, you made this. I'll finish it all.\N--Here's the peach lassi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:37.66,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sister wasn't the one making them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:41.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.21,Main,,0,0,0,,So immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.17,Main,,0,0,0,,He's really immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:50.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Just because you're an adult doesn't necessarily\Nmean you're mature. I thought you were aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.97,Main,,0,0,0,,"Closed for the Day."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.85,Main,,0,0,0,,"Closed for the Day."\NToday was our pre-opening, so I've closed the shop early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.93,Main,,0,0,0,,"Closed for the Day."\NThank you for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:06.31,Main,,0,0,0,,We were only open for half the day,\Nbut sales were excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It was harder than I expected. And very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.03,Main,,0,0,0,,We're not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:18.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I've prepared a barbecue to restore our\Nenergy since tomorrow will be a full day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.54,Main,,0,0,0,,--Meat?!\N--Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:21.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I want some, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. That much food is nothing. I'm a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Especially if you'll cook the meat for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:34.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone, the food's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.51,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You really don't learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,So immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:41.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, so enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Apologies. Is my cooking not to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:49.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I don't feel like eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:52.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm actually glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:56.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Food is so nourishing after hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji! Grill with the ratio of veggies, meat,\Nmeat, meat, meat, meat, meat, and fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Our profits today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:17.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, it looks so yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:27.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You were up early for work\Ntoday, huh? I came to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What? We're done already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:32.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Your sister is very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--I'm jealous since I'm an only child.\N--Would you like some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.99,Main,,0,0,0,,--You've told me that before!\N--Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.62,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:47.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not going to eat any meat?\NThat's not good. You won't grow bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I know! I'll make some for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,--Oh... Thank you very much.\N--Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,This might be the last straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no, barbecue should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Raw meat has more vitamins, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:15.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll call an ambulance, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Beach hut, Himitsu no Hanazono!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:29.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's the mango frappé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:32.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Phew. This is our last day working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,We made it through, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,But we didn't get to play at all,\Neven though we're at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.47,Main,,0,0,0,,We've been working this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:45.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you both for accompanying\Nme this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You got tan, Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,More like burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:53.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Even so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer means curry! Aren't I kind of like curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You're okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have a farmer's tan now,\Nso I want to even it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:06.66,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be done working, so let's go\Nall out and play tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,We haven't gone into the ocean,\Nso we need to take this chance now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty much done with homework,\Nso let's have fun for the rest of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:19.47,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Homewor--? I'm not sure I know that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:24.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Our modern Japanese homework is a\Nreflection essay. Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, I will prepare lunch for you as thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:30.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:32.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have any requests?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Barbecue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We had that the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the beach without barbecue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,There's more to the beach than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.45,Main,,0,0,0,,How about curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.66,Main,,0,0,0,,It's enough just looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:46.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You can leave it up to me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Regardless, let us enjoy the beach tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The ocean is plentiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,--You're going to catch stuff?!\N--All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:58.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's make the most out of tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.98,Main,,0,0,0,,"Shark Sighted\NNo Swimming"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:15.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It depends on the species,\Nfreshness, and cooking preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,--What the heck? I can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.20,Main,,0,0,0,,--What the heck? I can't swim!\N--How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It would have been nice if it were\Na dolphin rather than a shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:33.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not working today, right?\NYou can play, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what we thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.75,Main,,0,0,0,,--There's a shark--\N--Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"Southern Sea Resort Hotel"\NI brought tickets for the hotel pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So let's go here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:47.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:50.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we barbecue there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:53.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I said it was a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.10,Main,,0,0,0,,A pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.31,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:59.52,Main,,0,0,0,,It is all thanks to you, Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:02.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:06.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's been a while since\NI've gone to a pool with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, make sure to stretch. Here's a floatie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like you came with your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, where's Miss Sonobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:21.00,Main,,0,0,0,,The lunches are taking longer than expected.\NShe said she would meet us by lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, let's pla--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:24.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Usuda. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.56,Main,,0,0,0,,He's not good at dealing with Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I just happened to come here with my family. Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:42.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yu! I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:02.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It was probably emotional\Ndamage rather than physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:06.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sakura went with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:09.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:13.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, be nice to him next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:19.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's enjoy this pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,We will enjoy it in Yu's place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:35.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is amazing! Hotel pools are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:40.83,Main,,0,0,0,,But, it's so cool, Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:44.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Your bathing suit is pretty amazing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-This is normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, it's amazing you\Ngot free tickets for this pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama's sister gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:17:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,"First place"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.78,Main,,0,0,0,,"First place"\NIt's so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.91,Main,,0,0,0,,So that was Hayama's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, she gave me the tickets she won.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't really enjoy myself now that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:29.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like Hayama is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Hayama and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.56,Main,,0,0,0,,They're totally enjoying themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:40.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Just... ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,--They're totally enjoying themselves...\N--I-Ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Got some turban shells!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:57.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm practicing catching\Nsea urchin or abalone and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't do that here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:05.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's against the law\Nunless you're a fisherman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.34,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:15.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nishiyama. Why do you always\Nfollow me? No way, do you {\i1}like {\i0}me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:17.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't make up gross things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the nice girl from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:22.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hayama's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Even her sister's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she your friend, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:29.69,Main,,0,0,0,,She's just my classmate, Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! Since we're all here,\Nlet's all play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:33.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Wai--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I have some friends here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:46.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll go finish my sandcastle--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:47.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You should swim, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You should know. I can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:55.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, you can't swim, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:19:03.18,Main,,0,0,0,,It's pretty scary if something happens, huh.\NLike if your boat sinks in the middle of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's practice swimming!\NIn case you really need to some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,When I really need to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--There!\N--Like now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,--You can do it, Teru!\N--Th-The sisters share a resemblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:31.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, Teru. You need to try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:34.09,Main,,0,0,0,,No, way! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama, you don't like the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I just can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I've lasted this long not knowing\Nhow to swim. I'm fine just the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:49.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go practice in the kiddie pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,--You can do it!\N--Please try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.45,Main,,0,0,0,,--Everyone! I brought lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,--Everyone! I brought lunch.\N--Oh, Miss Sonobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:05.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You took a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:12.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it took me longer since there\Nwere so many unfamiliar things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.67,Main,,0,0,0,,This is your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it really took a while\Nsince it was a first for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, why are you both beat up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It was just harder than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:26.43,Main,,0,0,0,,And it was wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:30.02,Main,,0,0,0,,But, we got a hold of a rare ingredient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Rare ingredient?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't think the shark\Nwill be bothering us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:38.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I still don't recommend swimming\Nsince there are many jellyfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.63,Main,,0,0,0,,--Delish!\N--You ate it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,It's ground meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:19.99,Main,,0,0,0,,They seem like good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You do get sleepy after swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You can use me as a pillow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:32.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, you can lean on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:35.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That would be improper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:49.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't eat another bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,She would...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Was she sleep talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:54.86,Main,,0,0,0,,She's probably having a feast\Nin her dream right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:57.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I can have a feast if I sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:21:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:02.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep. Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:04.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Sleep. Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:08.54,Main,,0,0,0,,--I don't think you can sleep if you try that hard.\N--Go to sleep. Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,--Sleep. Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,--Miss Yoko...\N--Sleep. Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.38,0:22:18.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Sleep. Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Shino Sonobe.\NI'm the Nishikawa family's former maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The black-hearted class representative,\Nthe poor girl on a bread-crust diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:27.06,Main,,0,0,0,,and the walking black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:31.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Their "to each their own color" life is\Nso entertaini-- I mean, wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:35.65,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, listen to the "Rock Scissors Parade."\NRock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I'm pitch black inside{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I can't live in luxury{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:46.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if there's lots{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With three of us, we can eat it all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clever and smart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:56.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm living resolutely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:59.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With a full tummy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:02.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I spend my days{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:05.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What makes me smile?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:06.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Food!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.64,0:23:07.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Money..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I can't say here"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.14,0:23:12.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We each have our own happiness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's enjoy life as much as we want{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:16.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's crazy and messy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, it's the rock scissors parade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:22.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the three of us gather{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:24.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For rock, paper, scissors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll tie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:29.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it'll never end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The parade's started, and you have to join{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The answer to one times three{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:44.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you want to know, then come here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:49.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mumble mumble"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:51.97,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mumble mumble"\NI can't eat another bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:53.89,Main,,0,0,0,,But I can. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.89,0:23:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:58.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I cannot. I cannot eat anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:24:01.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I will take the rest to-go. I cannot?!
